description: Darley is one of the gym trainers from the Kantonian Gym in Malie City on Ula`ula Island in the Alola Region. He is specifically the guardian of the second floor of the gym. For his floor challenge, each person must finish a plate of food such as Octillery`s Special Breakfast Balls or the Goldeen Jelly Dessert. The point of challenging his floor is to let visitors know what Malie City has to offer guests.
